Berkshire’s Lubrizol Buys Active Organics to Bolster Cosmetics

-- B y   A n d r e w   F r y e
-- 
2011-12-12T19:07:02Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-12/berkshire-s-lubrizol-buys-active-organics-to-bolster-cosmetics.html
Berkshire Hathaway Inc. (BRK/A) ’s Lubrizol
Corp. agreed to buy Active Organics Inc. to add sales of
specialty ingredients, including botanical extracts used by
makers of cosmetics.  The deal for the Texas-based company will be completed this
year, according to a statement today from Lubrizol that didn’t
disclose terms.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andrew Frye in New York at 
 afrye@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dan Kraut at   dkraut2@bloomberg.net  